TY  - JOUR
T1  - Rethinking the Product Portfolio: A Generalized Investment Model
AU  - Devinney, Timothy M.
AU  - Stewart, David W.
Y1  - 1988/09/01
PY  - 1988
DA  - 1988/09/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.34.9.1080
